# The real work of this repo currently lives in _local/ (the template bundles, the
# authoring methodology, planning and strategy docs, session logs, and the artifact atlas).
# The user's global ~/.gitignore_global hides `_LOCAL/` everywhere; re-include it HERE so the
# work is version-controlled in this repo. (The final templates/ home is a separate, still-open
# decision; content stays under _local/ for now by choice.)
!_local/
!_local/**

# Keep tool caches and OS junk out, even under _local/.
.memsearch/
**/.impeccable/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# subagent-driven-development scratch ledger
.superpowers/
